review_blob: I hate hoppy beers and this one is just right for me.  Warm, malty and as they say, just enough hops to keep it from being sweet.  Id like less carbonation, but then thats true of about every beer I drink except cask aged ales.
beer_name: Big Sky Moose Drool Brown Ale

review_blob: My favorite of the strong ales.  Buy up enough in November to last until it comes out again.....
